<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="March2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">March,</orth> subst. 1) military movement, journey of soldiers: <bibl n="shak. jn 2.60" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 60</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 2.60" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 60</bibl> <bibl n="shak. jn 2.60" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 60</bibl> <bibl n="shak. jn 5.1.7" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.598" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 598</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 1.2.195" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 I, 2, 195</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.3.58" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 58</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.5.57" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.115" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 6, 115</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.6.87" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 6, 87</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.8" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.2.13" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 5.10.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 10, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.4.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 4, 3</bibl>. <cit><quote>to make a march:</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.3.8" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 3, 8</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mac 5.2.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 2, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 4.8.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 8, 30</bibl>.<lb />2) grave and solemn walk: <cit><quote>and with solemn m. goes slow and stately by them,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 1.2.201" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 2, 201</bibl></cit>.
